{"tid":1425084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑衣市民接連遇襲　警方接報四小時後才到北角","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:07:39.000Z","uid":288981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"310ddd039ef17ad6ced747ebd0c026db1730f62a","tid":1425084,"uid":288981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"黑衣市民接連遇襲 警方接報四小時後才到北角<br />\n2019-08-06 HKT 21:56<br />\n<br />\n有穿黑衫市民，昨晚分別在北角和荃灣被人用木棍、甚至用刀襲擊，雙方毆鬥。<br />\n其中在北角，警方證實，接報後大約四個小時，才有警員到場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473121-20190806.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473121-20190806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZtB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=c14c4176\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473121-20190806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=72bcfa13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473121-20190806.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察鍾意就玩失蹤、鍾意就隻眼開隻眼閉、鍾意就話你藏有攻擊性武器非法集結襲警暴動，你吹呀？"}]}